(22, 1, '2015-02-25 12:31:46', '2015-02-25 12:31:46', '<h1>Ruby On Rails Applications</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/blog">Blog</a></h2>\r\nBlogging application https://twinksblog.herokuapp.com/\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/geolocation">Geolocation</a></h2>\r\nRuby on rails app to get address,city,state from longitude,latitude http://geocodder.herokuapp.com/\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/dynamicUrl">Dynamic Url</a></h2>\r\nApplication is about Loading URLs to new window,using #RubyonRails,#AJAX,#JSON http://chargement.herokuapp.com/\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/upload_file">Upload File</a></h2>\r\nupload pdf file using paperclip gem\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/cucumber_test">Cucumber Test</a></h2>\r\nLearning TDD in Ruby on rails.\r\n\r\n<!-- Gems -->\r\n<h1>Ruby Gems</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/Gemathon-Chargers/password_mate">Password Mate</a></h2>\r\nA Gem to generate Strong Random Passwords for your applications. The gem would generate random password till it is strong enough.\r\n\r\n<!-- Angular projects -->\r\n<h1>AngularJS Applications</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/carrArchitect">CarrArchitect</a></h2>\r\nAngular app + back-end firebase.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="https://github.com/twinks14/codeschool_app">CodeSchool App</a></h2>\r\nLearning Angular from codeschool...!!!.\r\n\r\n<hr />', 'My Projects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-25 12:31:46', '2015-02-25 12:31:46', '', 2, 'http://twinkalsavani.com/?p=22', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(23, 1, '2015-02-25 12:33:47', '2015-02-25 12:33:47', '<hr />\r\n\r\n<div id="doc2" class="yui-t7">\r\n<div id="inner">\r\n<div id="hd">\r\n<div class="yui-gc">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h1>Twinkal Savani</h1>\r\n<h2>Ruby on rails developer, Open source contributor</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-u">\r\n<div class="contact-info"><!--\r\n<h3><a id="pdf" href="#">Download PDF</a></h3>\r\n-->\r\n<h3><a href="mailto:svnsavani0@gmail.com">svnsavani0@gmail.com</a></h3>\r\n<!--\r\n<h3>(+91) -84-52-848422</h3>\r\n-->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .contact-info -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gc -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// hd -->\r\n<div id="bd">\r\n<div id="yui-main">\r\n<div class="yui-b">\r\n<div class="yui-gf">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h2>Objective</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-u">\r\n<p class="enlarge">To seek the challenging position in Development environment that needs innovation, creativity, dedication and enable me to continue to work in a challenging and fast paced environment, leveraging my current knowledge and fostering creativity with many learning opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gf -->\r\n<div class="yui-gf">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h2>Skills</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-my">\r\n<div class="yui-u">\r\n<h2>Web Developer</h2>\r\nAssertively exploit wireless initiatives rather than synergistic core competencies.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-u">\r\n<h2>Interface Design</h2>\r\nCredibly streamline mission-critical value with multifunctional functionalities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-u">\r\n<h2>Project Direction</h2>\r\nProven ability to lead and manage a wide variety of design and development projects in team and independent situations.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gf -->\r\n<div>\r\n<div class="yui-gf">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h2>Technical</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="talent">\r\n	<li>Ruby on Rails</li>\r\n	<li>C#.net</li>\r\n	<li>C++</li>\r\n	<li>C</li>\r\n	<li>Java</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="talent">\r\n	<li>Jquery</li>\r\n	<li>AngularJS</li>\r\n	<li>Ajax</li>\r\n	<li>CSS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="talent">\r\n	<li>Oracle</li>\r\n	<li>Mysql</li>\r\n	<li>SQL Server 2010</li>\r\n	<li>Postgres</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class="talent">\r\n	<li>OS X</li>\r\n	<li>Windows XP/Vista</li>\r\n	<li>Linux/Unix</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style="clear: both;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gf-->\r\n<div class="yui-gf">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h2>Experience</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-u -->\r\n<div class="yui-my">\r\n\r\n<!--\r\n<div class="job">\r\n<h2>Tata Consultancy Services</h2>\r\n<h3>System Engineer</h3>\r\n<h4>2014-2015</h4>\r\nIntrinsicly enable optimal core competencies through corporate relationships. Phosfluorescently implement worldwide vortals and client-focused imperatives. Conveniently initiate virtual paradigms and top-line convergence.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="job">\r\n<h2>Tata Consultancy Services</h2>\r\n<h3>Assistant System Engineer</h3>\r\n<h4>2013-2014</h4>\r\nRuby on rails developer following agile methodology.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n-->\r\n<div class="job last">\r\n<h2>Tata Consultancy Services.</h2>\r\n<h3>Ruby on Rails Developer</h3>\r\n<h4>From 2013</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Worked extensively with Ruby on Rails and Postgresql, mysql, oracle on the backend.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Experience with HTML5, Javascript, Angularjs, CSS3 and Twitter Bootstrap on the front end.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Active involvement in product backlog grooming, release / sprint planning, estimation, customer review meetings.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Direct Client and Product Owner Interaction.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Implementation of stories using best engineering practices.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Automated test cases such as Rspec, cucumber</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Deployment / Support Transition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ILP(Initial Learning Program)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">ILP(Initial Learning Program),is a training program for about 3 months,which every fresher has to undergo upon joining TCS.</li>\r\n	<li style="border-bottom: 0px;">Cource included: C#.net, SQL server 2010, HTML, JavaScript</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-u -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gf -->\r\n<div class="yui-gf last">\r\n<div class="yui-u first">\r\n<h2>Education</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-my">\r\n<h2>Gujarat Technological University - Gujarat, India</h2>\r\nMCA- Master of computer application — <strong>8.81 CGPA</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="yui-my">\r\n<h2>Bhavnagar University - Gujarat, India</h2>\r\nBCA- Bachelor of computer application — <strong>First Class</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-gf -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// .yui-b -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// yui-main -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// bd -->\r\n<div id="ft">\r\n\r\nTwinkal Savani — <a href="mailto:svnsavani0@gmail.com">svnsavani0@gmail.com</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// footer -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- // inner -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!--// doc -->', 'My Profile', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'profile', '', '', '2015-02-26 09:27:52', '2015-02-26 09:27:52', '', 0, 'http://twinkalsavani.com/?page_id=23', 0, 'page', '', 0),
